#X text 3 447 The "front" of the sound field at 0° or 0 rad azimuth, f 65;
#X text 3 462 The "left" of the sound field at 90 ° or π/2 rad azimuth, f 65;
#X text 3 476 The "back" of the sound field at 180° or π rad azimuth, f 65;
